{
  "stem": "7873.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In Warsaw, everybody could make-- anybody could make a living.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But not in a province-- little town, like I was born-- I was from.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Poland wasn't a big country to begin with.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You take any kind of little town, they're all near Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One-- like, what people used to do to better themselves, they went into Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of the German Jews were foreigners.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of them were born there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's-- when you went to Germany, you bettered yourself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like we lived near East Prussia, Konigsberg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the-- today, it's no more Konigsberg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's Kaliningrad.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Russians still have it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They'll never give it back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's the best part of Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I belonged to a, a [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The reason I belonged there-- because there-- friends of mine belonged there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were older than me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They, they-- we-- and so just to kill time, we belonged to that organization.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had a, a leader.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was-- there, there was also all kinds of organizations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had Betar, Bund.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but I was too young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to buy a little ball and go out in the field on a farm someplace.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We used to play.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's like-- we were crazy for it, like in-- baseball in this country.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Soccer.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We used to play baseball, too, but in a different way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the-- you, you start a, a, a pitcher.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did-- pitched ourself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, it was a lot of fun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it wasn't as popular as it is here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father said the-- my father said the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, that he's-- that I'm-- in one word, that I'm on my own.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
